
program: WordCoun with Spark Framework


Prerequisites:
=========================================
java JDK +7
spark 1.5.0 Framework
maven +2
=========================================
create our project with maven tool
=========================================
create project maven:
mvn archetype:generate
 -DgroupId=com.spark.app
 -DartifactId=spark
 -DarchetypeArtifactId=maven-archetype-quickstart
 -DinteractiveMode=false
build our project :
  cd spark
  mvn package
============================================
Steps to run this project
============================================
example to input and output file:
        input hdfs://localhost:8020/user/hdfs/test
        output hdfs://localhost:8020/user/hdfs/rst

/home/../spark/bin/spark-submit --class com.spark.App arg1 arg2 --master local[2] taget/jar

